{"tid":326162,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一碗好白粥，更要花心機","createTime":"2017-07-17T18:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T18:27:05.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bddeaee977bef63ec926a8fdfe3bbdb2f8998e14","tid":326162,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/022654_c8a631ed930f8e35e08e01cc937b3752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F022654_c8a631ed930f8e35e08e01cc937b3752.jpg&h=2c3de771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白粥就是不一樣。沒有花巧食材，就是米。粥一上桌，先觀其賣相，表面帶一點焦黑，不及格。粥色呈象牙白、米白或米黃，亦通統不及格，只有是粥色純白不帶半點雜質，才是第一關。之後是氣味，好的白粥要嘗到米香。接着再是稠度，舀起一匙，多餘的粥後匙邊緩慢地流下，且形成小團，才是好。最後，吃一口，米花要半溶半爛，質感幼細綿滑，散發淡淡米香，便是一碗好白粥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ustoq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ustoq0&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJijA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e1195199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ustoq0</a>"}]}